@startuml loginSequenceDiagram_1
title Login Flow

actor User
participant "React Frontend" as FE
participant "Ory Oathkeeper" as Oathkeeper
participant "Ory Kratos" as Kratos
participant "Spring Boot Backend" as BE

== Session Check on Mount ==

FE -> Oathkeeper : GET api.irboard.local/v1/whoami\n+ Cookie: (none)\n[rule: api-backend-protected\nauthenticator: cookie_session]
Oathkeeper -> Kratos : GET /sessions/whoami\n(cookie_session authenticator\nforwards cookie to Kratos)
Kratos --> Oathkeeper : 401 Unauthorized\n{ error: { code: 401,\n"No active session was found" } }
Oathkeeper --> FE : 401 Unauthorized\n(authenticator rejected,\naccess denied)

note over FE : isAuthenticated = false\nProceed to login flow

==  ==

@enduml